scene.message:
Yukino: It's an odd thing to{nl}
say in the afterlife, but...{nl}
I hope everyone gets home{nl}
safe.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey, hey, maybe there{nl}
are chests with "Mirror{nl}
Shards" in them too!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Still, the enemies here{nl}
are strong. Without proper{nl}
equipment{waitkey}we won't beat Yuriko.{waitkey}

Brown: Just like Cerberus{nl}
said, this Tartarus is{nl}
rough...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Checking every chest{nl}
would be hard on our time, I{nl}
fear.{waitkey}Open this chest?{nl}
{ctl0e:0}{ret}Got a "Mirror Shard"!{waitkey}{ret}
